{"tid":1198200,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[11~12/6]請求德國介入","createTime":"2019-06-10T07:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T15:57:49.000Z","uid":19557,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6106c2971fbe5e610eeb4739f39af8fe5420f1","tid":1198200,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家既情況單單靠香港人自己係唔夠力，所以我希望11號或者12號參與任何遊行或行動既朋友可以自備印有以下中文德文雙語既紙牌到時舉起比各國傳媒影低 (德文要大過中文) </span><br />\n<br />\n條例通過之後 NGO 係香港會十分危險 等同NGO失去一個亞洲重要基地 影響深遠<br />\nWenn das Auslieferungsgesetz verabschiedet wird, sind NGOs in Hongkong gef&auml;hrdet.<br />\nDies bedeutet, dass NGOs eine wichtige Basis in Asien verlieren werden.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場唔單止係香港人既戰爭 仲係自由世界同極權世界既戰爭<br />\nDies ist nicht nur ein Krieg in Hongkong, sondern auch ein Krieg zwischen der freien Welt und dem Totalitarismus<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共政府唔理100萬民意<br />\nDie Regierung in Hongkong ignoriert die Stimmen von 1Millionen Menschen<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n停止修訂逃犯條例<br />\nStoppt das Auslieferungsgesetz! (Stop or no extradition law)"},{"pid":"df4925fba4a6308129d829c8db3e97785415de32","tid":1198200,"uid":19557,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"感謝 一馬 巴/絲打同佢另一半提供德文翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631fab3725a20df0e07f62c7f55b27cfbd90838e","tid":1198200,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e00cbedae7e27eaabde4a4bbf66c0896e8003bd6","tid":1198200,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4de4eda7ffeb1481d07c98d55956b2168e60a383","tid":1198200,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"